CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 26, 1958, pg. B5 reads: " Metoka Contestants - Six of the 12 contestants awarded scholarships totaling $1,346.50 by the Metoka Club are shown above. First row; Barbara Mills, Marcia Hord and Faye Benson.  Last row: Joseph Golden, Dennis Hudson and Arenzo R. Smith. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of scholarship winners, front row: Barbara Mills, Marcia Hord, and Faye Benson; back row: Joseph Golden, Dennis Hudson, and Arenzo R. Smith, posed in front of Lemington Avenue Home for Aged Women for Metoka Club garden party
